snippet.title: Space station game - Galaxy Pass Station - Gameplay Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
This is a space station game and a new gameplay trailer of the Galaxy Pass Station game. About the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1571990/Galaxy_Pass_Station/?utm_source=youtube

Our game is a space station simulator game and is a simulation of building your base in the form of a space station where aliens arrive. Our games similar to papers please, yes yes, checking documents is an essential part of the game. And our games similar to oxygen not included, the settlement requires resources and you have various challenges in outer space.
